no_op.no_token_for_existing_keys: Dibaginjigewin aazha gii-izhinizha’igaade imaa ogimaa-mazinaabikiwebiniganing. verification_code_info.info_body:
Giga-odaapinamaagoo minomanji’owi-ogimaawiwin, {{healthAuthorityName}}, gidaginaasobii’igan giishpin gagweji’igooyan GOOBID-19 geget inaapineyan. 

Mii owe ge-inaabadak gidagindaasobii’igan, ji-zoongitooyaang gagweji’igooyan GOOBID-19 geget inaapineyan. 

Ajina eta go da-anokiimagad gidagindaasobii’igan. 

Giishpin gegoo maazhisemagak megwaa maajinizha’aman gidagindaasobii’igan, oshki-agindaasobii’igan gidaa-odaapinamaagoo jibwaa-gojitooyan miinawaa.
verification_code_info.what_happens_body:
Apii gidagindaasobii’igan maajinizha’aman, giga-gagwejimigoo ji-zoongitooyan nakongeyan gikendaagozisiwan ji-maada’ookiiyan igiw aaniind gewiinawaa maagizhaa gii-odisigowaad. 

Giishpin bagidinaman, giga-maada’ookii bagwana asigibii’iganan ji-gikendang awiya gaa-nakweshkawad gii-odisigod GOOBID-19. Mii dash wewiib ge-izhi-nandawaabandang endazhi-gagweji’iweng miinawaa ji-ganawenjiged minomanji’owin.

exposure_history.exposure_summary: Ingoji go {{startDate}} biinish igo {{endDate}} gigii-nakweshkawaa awiya gii-gagweji’igod GOOBID-19 geget inaapined.
exposure_history.how_does_this_work_para: Giishpin baakinaman Wiindamaagewinan Gaa-odisigoyan, giga-maada’ookii bagwana asigibii’iganan (Random IDs gaa-izhinikaadegin) apii nakweshkawad bakaan awiya owe app aabajitood giishpin Wiindamaagewinan Gaa-odisigoyan baakinang gewiin. Ozhaawashkwaabid aabadad imaa gigiigidowining owe ji-izhichigaadeg. Gaawiin dash giga-gikendaagozisii. Moozhag aanjibii’igaadewan Random IDs.
exposure_history.no_exposure_reports_over_past: Gaawiin gegoo dibaajimowin odisigoyan gigii-odaapinanziin 14 dasogon gaa-izhiseg
exposure_history.why_did_i_get_an_en_para: Giga-wiindamaagoo gaa-odisigoyan giishpin nakweshkawad awiya dibaadodang gagweji’iwed GOOBID-19 geget inaapined owe app aabajitood.

protect_privacy.body_1: Gaawiin ganage dagonigaadesinoon iwe gikenjigewin ji-gikendaagoziyan onow IDs, miinawaa gaye moozhag aanjibii’igaadewan.
protect_privacy.body_2: Gimaada’ookii bagwana asigibii’iganan ji-gikenjigaadeg apii nakweshkawad awiya endaso-giizhig, Ozhaawashkwaabid aabadak owe ji-izhichigaadeg. Aabijibide {{applicationName}} geyaabi giishpin giba’aman.
protect_privacy.body_3: Giishpin gagweji’igooyan GOOBID-19 geget inaapineyan, agindaasobii’igan gidaa-maajinizha’aan imaa {{applicationName}} ji-zoongitooyan inaapineyan. Random IDs imaa gigiigidowining maajinizha’igaadewan ogimaa-mazinaabikiwebiniganing. Mii owe ezhichigeyaang ji-zoongitooyaang gagweji’igooyan GOOBID-19 geget inaapineyan.
protect_privacy.body_4: Giishpin mikaajigaadeg ID gaa-dibendang awiya GOOBID-19 geget enaapined, naasaab ID imaa gigiigidowining mikaajigaadeg, maagizhaa gigii-nakweshkawaa awiya enaapined. Mii owe ge-izhi-gikenjigaadeg giishpin odisigoyan {{applicationName}} aabajitooyan.
protect_privacy.body_5:
Giishpin odisigoyan iwe oshki-aakoziwin, {{applicationName}} giga-wiindamaag aaniish ge-izhichigeyamban, minomaji’owi-ogimaawiwin gaa-ikidowaad. 

Mii owe inake enaabadak {{applicationName}} ji-gikendamamban aaniish inake ge-izhi-ganawenindizowamban maagizhaa gaye ji-ganawenimadwaaban giiji-bimaadiziig, ji-gikendaagozisiwan gaye zhaage ji-gikenjigaadesinok aandi gwayak gaa-izhaayan.

emergency_symptoms.select_any: Onaabandan gakina inamanji’oyan (gemaa gaye gaawiin gegoo).

guidance.dont_go_to_work: Gego izhaaken iwidi endananokiiyan, gikinoo’amaadiiwigamigong, maagizhaa gaye ingoji agwajayi’ii.
guidance.drink_water: De-minikwen nibi miinawaa gegoo gaa-biinaagamig ji-baagosesiwan.
guidance.find_telehealth: Aabajitoon gigiigidowin maagizhaa gaye gimazinaabikiwebinigan ji-nanaandawi’igooyan
guidance.follow_cdc_guidance: Giishpin ani-maanamanji’oyan, mii go izhi-biminizha’an iwe CDC ayaangwaami-doodamowinan.
guidance.if_symptoms_develop: Giishpin GOOBID-19 ani-inamanji’oyan maagizhaa gaye nawaj ani-maanamanji’oyan wayiiba ganoozh awe gaa-nanaandawi’iwed.
guidance.monitor_your_symptoms: Maanendaagwad maanamanji’oyan. Gidaa-nazhikewab dedibaabandizoyan.  Giishpin nawaj ani-maanamanji’oyan gidaa-ganoonaa awe gaa-nanaandawi’iwed, nazhikewabin.
guidance.seek_medical_care: Giishpin gegoo ani-izhiseg maagizhaa gaye nawaj maanamanji’oyan, gidaa-odisaa gaa-nanaandawi’iwed.
guidance.stay_6_feet_away: Ganage ingodwaasozid gidaa-dawigaabawitaage, gego dash gaye izhaaken ingoji bayaatayiiniyong.
guidance.stay_at_home: Nazhikewabin, mii eta go ji-odisad gaa-nanaandawi’iwed ge-izhaayan agwajing.
guidance.stay_away_from_higher_risk_people: Giishpin gashkitooyan, gego odisaaken awiya gaa-wenipanizid GOOBID-19 ji-inaapined.
guidance.take_care_of_yourself: Nandagikendan inake ge-izhi-ganawenindizowamban maagizhaa gaye ge-izhi-ganawenimadiban awiya ani-aakozid.
guidance.take_temperature: Dibaabandizon epiichi-gizhizoyan niizhing endaso-giizhig.  Dedibaabandizon gaye GOOBID-19 ji-ni-inamanji’oyan.
guidance.you_have_underlying_conditions: Maanendaagwad maanamanji’oyan. Maagizhaa GOOBID-19 gidinaapine. Gidinaapine dash gaye aanind nawaj ji-wenipaniziyan wiinge ji-maanamanji’oyan odisigoyan oshki-aakoziwin GOOBID-19 gaa-izhinikaadeg.

intro.find_out_how_to_care: Nandagikendan inake ge-izhi-ganawenindizowamban maagizhaa gaye ge-izhi-ganawenimadiban awiya giishpin nakweshkawadiban GOOBID-19 geget gaa-inaapined

intro.this_is_based_on: Owe gikenjigewin onzikaamagad imaa CDC ezhinikaadeg, aayaapii go naa da-aanjisemagad iwe gikenjigewin nawaj bi-gikendamaang aanish inake ezhiwebizid awe dinowa oshki-aakozi-manijooshens
intro.this_is_not_intended: Gaawiin ganage owe aabajichigan da-inaabadasinoon ji-gikendaagoziyan giishpin geget inaapineyan iwe oshki-aakoziwin, zhaage ji-nanaandawi’igooyan
intro.you_are_a_resident: Gidizhi-daa imaa endananokiiwaad {{ healthAuthorityName }}, igiw ji-bami’ikwaa

settings.delete_data_disclosure1: Apii daangibii’aman “Gaasibii’an Indibaginjigewin” gakina dibaginjigewin imaa  {{applicationName}} da-gaasibii’igaade:
settings.delete_data_disclosure2:
Gaawiin dash da-gaasibii’igaadesinoon iwe gaa-ozhichigaadeg imaa gigiigidowining Wiindamaagewinan Gaa-odisigoyan wezhibii’igaadeg. 

Mii imaa Onaabandamowinan app gigiigidowining ge-dazhi-gaasibii’aman.
settings.delete_data_language_token: Aawechigaans imaa gigiigidowining eteg aabajichigaade gidinwewin ji-gikendaagwak
settings.delete_data_onboarding_token: Aawechigaans imaa gigiigidowining eteg aabajichigaade app-boozichigaazoyan ji-gikendaagwak
settings.delete_data_product_analytics: Aawechigaans imaa gigiigidowining eteg aabajichigaade nakongeyan ji-maada’ookiiyan ji-gikendaagwak
settings.delete_data_this_action: Giga-gaasibii’aan gakina gegoo {{applicationName}} gaa-dazhibii’igaadeg giishpin doodaman owe.

verification_code_alerts.invalid_code_body:
Gaawiin geyaabi onizhishinzinoon iwe agindaasobii’igan gaa-maajinizha’aman. 

Memwech igo wenizhishing agindaasobii’igan minomanji’owi-ogimaawiwin gaa-odaapinamaagooyan gidaa-aabajitoon. 

Maagizhaa gaye ishkwaataamagad gidagindaasobii’igan. Giishpin debwemagak owe, bakaan agindaasobii’igan gidaa-andotamaag minomanji’owi-ogimaawiwin.
verification_code_alerts.network_connection_body: Memwech igo da-aanikoosin WiFi gigiigidowin agindaasobii’igan ji-maajinizha’aman.
verification_code_alerts.no_keys_on_device_body: Gaawiin debisesinoon gaa-ako-aabajitooyan owe app odisigoyan ji-maada’ookiiyan. Geyaabi nazhikewabin.
verification_code_alerts.no_keys_on_device_title: Gaawiin gegoo wedisigoyan gidayaanziin ji-maada’ookiiyan omaa giigidowining
verification_code_alerts.not_authorized_body: Gaawiin gibagidinanziin owe app Random IDs ji-maada’ookiimagak.
verification_code_alerts.rate_limit_body: Gaawiin geyaabi gegoo gidaa-maajinizha’anziin noongom gaa-giizhigak. 24 daso-diba’igan baabiitoon jibwaa-gojitooyan miinawaa.
